label: How do I contact an organizer?
content: Through our Discord! Join using the button above!

label: How many people can be on a team?
content: HackUTA Teams consist of four members per team. You can either apply with a team, or apply without a team and get matched with one for the event.

label: How long do we have to work on our projects?
content: Hacking begins October 4th at 12:00 PM and ends October 5th at 12:00 PM. You will have 24 hours to work on your project.

label: Will there be food?
content: We will provide lunch, dinner, breakfast, and a final lunch, times will be available on the schedule above.

label: Where is the event?
content: The event is being held at the SWSH and SEIR at UTA!
